08:19.565 --> 08:21.402
You did?

08:21.402 --> 08:22.605
Oh, they're good.

08:22.605 --> 08:24.075
This is good.

08:24.075 --> 08:26.045
Oh, this is real good.

08:26.045 --> 08:28.049
- I'm trying to get
back to Okern, okay?
