with the well water.

17:58.489 --> 18:01.462
- Oh, my gosh, man...
- Oh, well, if your body's

18:01.462 --> 18:03.098
not used to it,
you could experience

18:03.098 --> 18:05.570
- some minor difficulties.
- Like what?

18:05.570 --> 18:09.110
