right to the highway.

18:41.910 --> 18:44.381
What do you mean,
if anything happens?

18:44.381 --> 18:48.455
Well, you never know. Do you?

18:50.627 --> 18:52.965
They got spiders in there?

18:52.965 --> 18:54.635
Nah, just snakes.

18:54.635 --> 18:57.574
- Couple of dead cats.
